product.description: NOPE is a prototype tote bag featuring a cute & fiery demon. The print is printed by hand with a hand cut lino stamp. As a prototype these have some printing issues and are not perfect but would still make a lovely and sassy bag to hall your books or snacks. Limited Edition.
